@baseUrl = http://localhost:18080/api

### 1. Ping Test
GET {{baseUrl}}/ping

### 2. List All Clusters
GET {{baseUrl}}/clusters

### 3. Create a New Cluster
POST {{baseUrl}}/clusters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Local ES Cluster",
  "hosts": ["http://localhost:9200"],
  "color": "#18a058",
  "notes": "Testing via .http file"
}

### 4. Get Single Cluster (Replace ID)
# @name createCluster
GET {{baseUrl}}/clusters/9cca561e-80e3-4420-a52b-945e69bb72d0

### 5. Delete Cluster (Replace ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/clusters/9cca561e-80e3-4420-a52b-945e69bb72d0
